OL,3,CNo guarantee on tax rebate for
OL,4,Cresidents over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FThe man at Birmingham City Council
OL,7,Fresponsible for the city's waste
OL,8,Fservice tells ITV News Central that
OL,9,Fthey need to 'sort it out'.
OL,11,FA Birmingham City Council boss has
OL,12,Ftold ITV News Central the majority of
OL,13,Fbin workers have accepted the
OL,14,Fcouncil's offers despite the bin
OL,15,Fstrikes continuing.
OL,17,FCraig Cooper, the council's Strategic
OL,18,FDirector of City Operation, insists
OL,19,Fthey're keen to get back around the
OL,20,Ftable with Unite to resolve the
OL,21,Fdispute as soon as possible.
