OL,3,CNo guarantee on tax rebate for
OL,4,Cresidents over Birmingham bin strikes
OL,6,FMr Cooper told ITV News Central:
OL,7,F"We're offering them a fair deal, and
OL,8,Fwe're giving them an opportunity to
OL,9,Fstick with the council and stay with
OL,10,Fthe council."
OL,12,FMr Cooper has not committed to a tax
OL,13,Frebate, and is hoping Unite workers
OL,14,Fagree to the Council's terms soon.
OL,16,FHe said: "I really need Unite to look
OL,17,Fat how things have progressed over the
OL,18,Flast six weeks, see the feelings on
OL,19,Fthe streets."
