OL,6,FHowever, Birmingham City Council had
OL,7,Fpreviously said 17 workers will lose
OL,8,Fout on #6,000.
OL,10,FWhen asked about the disparity, Mr
OL,11,FCooper said: "We started a
OL,12,Fconsultation with 170 people and with
OL,13,FUnite last September. 130 people have
OL,14,Feither accepted progression and the
OL,15,Fopportunity to do driver training, or
OL,16,Fhave accepted to do roles in the
OL,17,Fequivalent of a grade 3.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
