OL,6,F"There are 40 individuals that have
OL,7,Fnot accepted to move into an equal
OL,8,Frole. If they wish to remain working
OL,9,Fon the bins.
OL,11,F"There will be a driver and two
OL,12,Floaders, if they wish to remain in a
OL,13,Floader they'll have to move into a
OL,14,Fgrade 2 role. They don't have to lose
OL,15,Fout, they can move into another grade
OL,16,F3 role into the city operations.
OL,18,F"A proportion of people have taken
OL,19,Fredundancy, a proportion have taken
OL,20,Fdriver training and driver advancement.
