OL,6,F"We really urge this last group to
OL,7,Ftake one of the 3 options we've
OL,8,Fadvised. I'd really urge them to take
OL,9,Fone of these as they don't have to
OL,10,Fdrop to a grade 2."
OL,12,F"That's 40 people (we're negotiating
OL,13,Fwith) out of 17 of them, if 17 of them
OL,14,Fwish to move down to grade 2 loaders
OL,15,Fthen they will lose out by about
OL,16,F#6,000. But we're not advocating that,
OL,17,Fwe're offering an equal job in another
OL,18,Fpart of city operations."
