OL,6,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,7,FNational Lead Officer at Unite says
OL,8,Fthe union will "make no apology" for
OL,9,Fdefending its members
OL,11,FUnite has now suggested bin strikes,
OL,12,Flike the ones seen in Birmingham over
OL,13,Fthe past five weeks, could spread to
OL,14,Fother areas in the UK.
