OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Central, Onay
OL,7,FKasab, National Lead Officer at Unite
OL,8,Fsaid: "The fact is, austerity measures
OL,9,Fare continuing in local authorities
OL,10,Fbecause of the underfunding crisis in
OL,11,Flocal authorities, if those employers
OL,12,Fmove to attack our members pay and
OL,13,Fconditions then we make no apology for
OL,14,Fthat fact that we will defend those
OL,15,Fmembers."
